"Bloomberg Enterprise" profiles  Ethan
Allen Interiors Inc. (ETH) , a North American furniture chain with 281 
stores across the  United States .  This program features an interview with M. Farooq Kathwari,
chief executive officer of Ethan Allen. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 21:19
 